### 회원가입 - 토큰 없이 가능
POST http://localhost:8080/api/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userid": "test01",
  "passwd": "1234",
  "username": "테스트사용자",
  "email": "test01@example.com"
}

### 로그인 - Access Token + Refresh Token 발급
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userid": "admin",
  "passwd": "admin1234"
}

### 아래 변수는 IntelliJ HTTP Client에서 로그인 응답의 accessToken 값을 복사해서 넣으세요.
@accessToken = 여기에_accessToken_붙여넣기
@refreshToken = 여기에_refreshToken_붙여넣기

### 내 정보 조회
GET http://localhost:8080/api/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 전체 조회 - JWT 필요
GET http://localhost:8080/api/users
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 아이디 검색 - JWT 필요
GET http://localhost:8080/api/users?keyword=user
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 단건 조회 - JWT 필요
GET http://localhost:8080/api/users/admin
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 수정 - JWT 필요
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/users/test01
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "passwd": "5678",
  "username": "수정사용자",
  "email": "test01-updated@example.com"
}

### 삭제 - JWT 필요
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/users/test01
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Access Token 재발급 - Refresh Token 사용, Refresh Token도 회전 발급
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/refresh
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refreshToken": "{{refreshToken}}"
}

### 로그아웃 - Refresh Token 폐기
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/logout
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refreshToken": "{{refreshToken}}"
}
